# Day 3: Data Integration and Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) Project

## Introduction
This notebook focuses on Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) and data integration methodologies aimed at enhancing operational efficiency in Manufacturing Execution Systems (MES), Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP), and Internet of Things (IoT) systems. Additionally, a mini-project on analyzing the production quality data from Epson will be covered, demonstrating practical EDA techniques.

