6. Mini Project: Epson Production Quality Analysis

## 1. Data Loading
In this section, we will load the data into our environment using Pandas.

```python
import pandas as pd

# Load the production quality dataset
data = pd.read_csv('path_to_your_data.csv')
```

## 2. Data Inspection
Now we will display the first few rows of the dataset and check its structure.

```python
# Display the first five rows of the dataset
print(data.head())

# Check the data types and missing values
print(data.info())
```

## 3. Data Cleaning
This step involves handling missing values and duplicates in the dataset.

```python
# Fill missing values
data.fillna(method='ffill', inplace=True)

# Remove duplicates
data.drop_duplicates(inplace=True)
```

## 4. Data Transformation
Transform the data as necessary to prepare it for analysis.

```python
# Example Transformation: Convert date columns
data['Production_Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Production_Date'])
```

## 5. Data Visualization
Visualizing the data to identify patterns and insights.

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

# Set the aesthetic style of the plots
sns.set_style("whitegrid")

# Example Visualization: Production Quality over Time
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
sns.lineplot(data=data, x='Production_Date', y='Quality_Score')
plt.title('Production Quality Over Time')
plt.xlabel('Date')
plt.ylabel('Quality Score')
plt.show()
```

